{"tid":1794110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中日韓經貿部長會議確認 推動2020年簽署RCEP","createTime":"2019-12-23T01:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:57:38.000Z","uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3a985592dd02bd161d8966aab1e8783329b27a","tid":1794110,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:26:19.000Z","msg":"上報    國際中心<br />\n2019年12月23日 上午8:14<br />\n<br />\n中日韓經貿部長會議22日在北京召開，三方同意積極推動2020年內簽署區域全面經濟夥伴<br />\n關係協定（RCEP）。除了同意簽署協定外，三方也確認反對任何形式的保護主義。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》報導，中國商務部長鐘山表示，中日韓要共同反對單邊主義和貿易保護主義，<br />\n進一步提升貿易投資合作水平。根據日本《共同社》，日本經濟產業相梶山弘志表示，將<br />\n加快中日韓自由貿易協定（FTA）談判。<br />\n<br />\nRCEP談判11月初在印度宣布退出後呈現僵局，日本一度強烈表示沒有印度，不簽署協定也<br />\n罷。梶山弘志稱將努力讓印度參與在內。此外，日韓因半導體材料出口管制而關係惡化，<br />\n當日會議結束後，日韓雙方官員短暫談話，不過並未透露具體內容。<br />\n<br />\n這是自2016年10月在東京舉行以來，時隔約3年再次召開中日韓經貿部長會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/qpyx4ge\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fqpyx4ge&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=26a05317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/qpyx4ge</a>"},{"pid":"e395d381215839e9a6341f5e2dd76e02efb3421a","tid":1794110,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"日本仔，泡菜做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6675c6bec29867bbb2f8f932dcd4d5d36e64631","tid":1794110,"uid":75556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"01就咪放LIN啦"},{"pid":"933d4ae7829cd4a8663dad5d2e285f5f32ec811f","tid":1794110,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國聯邦議